#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn2.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Anāthapiṇḍikavagga "
msgstr "2. With Anāthapiṇḍika "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Veṇḍusutta "
msgstr "12. With Vishnu "

# NOTE: There seems no reason not to use the well-known Sanskritic form here.
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: veṇḍu → veṇhu (bj, pts2)
msgctxt "sn2.12:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho veṇḍu devaputto bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Standing to one side, the god Vishnu recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

# NOTE: Maybe it’s excessive, but I wonder whether in this rare appearance of Vishnu it’s not relevant that he mentions Manu?
#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: Sukhitāva te → sukhitā vata te (bj, s1-3, km, pts2)
msgctxt "sn2.12:2.1"
msgid "“Sukhitāva te manujā, "
msgstr "“Happy are the children of Manu "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.12:2.2"
msgid "sugataṃ payirupāsiya; "
msgstr "who pay homage to the Holy One! "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Yuñjaṃ → yuñja (s1-3, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn2.12:2.3"
msgid "Yuñjaṃ gotamasāsane, "
msgstr "They apply themselves to Gotama’s instructions, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.12:2.4"
msgid "appamattā nu sikkhare”ti. "
msgstr "diligently training.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.119, sc3
#. VAR: siṭṭhipade → satthipade (bj, s1-3, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn2.12:3.1"
msgid "“Ye me pavutte siṭṭhipade, "
msgstr "“Those who practice absorption in accord with the training”, "

#. HTML: <span class="speaker">
msgctxt "sn2.12:3.2"
msgid "(veṇḍūti bhagavā) "
msgstr "said the Buddha to Vishnu, "

#. HTML: </span><br>
msgctxt "sn2.12:3.3"
msgid "Anusikkhanti jhāyino; "
msgstr "“in the way of teaching I’ve proclaimed, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.12:3.4"
msgid "Kāle te appamajjantā, "
msgstr "they’re in time to be diligent; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.12:3.5"
msgid "Na maccuvasagā siyun”ti. "
msgstr "they won’t fall under the sway of Death.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
